description.en: TacoSwap is a Dex Defi protocol & Yield Farm, designed to be the next evolution. Taking Sushiswap’s liquidity focused strategy, they have added fiat on-ramp and off-ramp and rewards for liquidity providers while improving the payout rate to 0.5%. The project is integrated under the Ethereum Smart Chain. Its token eTaco-V2 has a limited supply of 395 million tokens.
